<h3>Ajax Search</h3>
<p align="justify">In order to configure this module, you should navigate to Magento admin panel and choose the <strong>Stores > Configuration</strong> section in the left side menu.</p>
<p>Then choose the <strong> TemplateMonster > Catalog Search Ajax</strong> item  in the left side menu to go to the module settings interface.</p>
 <figure class="img-polaroid"><img src="img/magento/search.png" alt="" /></figure>

<div class="alert alert-info">  <p> <i class="fa fa-info-circle" style="font-size:24px"></i> Check the tutorial on <a href="https://zemez.io/magento/support/how-to/magento-2-1-x-how-to-manage-ajax-search-module/">  How to Manage Ajax Search Module</a>.</p></div>
